description:
Rilynn is athletic, young, and full of promise. She outweighs Lyla, and has a background in track which gives her stamina.
Lyla is, well, our best loser, but in Season 10 she is determined to get her cock sucked in Round 4 at least once.
title: Lyla "The Jaguar" Storm vs Rilynn "The Rattler" Rae
